        {
            "comment": "When exogenous_maxTAir == -999 and exogenous_minTAir == 999, Estimate returns sentinel outputs (maxTSoil = -999, minTSoil = 999) and resets deeplayerstates_deepLayerT to 0.0."
        },
        {
            "comment": "ratesexternal_heatFlux is interpreted as g m-2 d-1 and is converted to MJ m-2 d-1 via SoilAvailableEnergy = soilHeatFlux * lambda_ / 1000."
